 How disloyal of me. 

263
00:22:16,640 --> 00:22:19,020
It is my fault.

264
00:22:20,520 --> 00:22:23,380
- What? 
 - I was absorbed into my emotions

265
00:22:23,380 --> 00:22:27,470
that I did not think you would feel upset.

266
00:22:27,470 --> 00:22:32,350
So, I would like to apologize formally.

267
00:22:32,350 --> 00:22:35,480
- What? 
 - Please wait a moment.

268
00:22:36,100 --> 00:22:38,190
Wait...

269
00:22:48,660 --> 00:22:50,420
By chance...

270
00:22:56,300 --> 00:22:58,990
- Again? 
 - "Teachers are endlessly generous."

271
00:22:58,990 --> 00:23:03,550
Teachers are endlessly generous. One cannot even step on their shadows.

272
00:23:03,550 --> 00:23:07,750
This foolish student dared to hurt your feelings.

273
00:23:07,750 --> 00:23:11,450
Nothing can possibly make you forgive me, but...

274
00:23:12,510 --> 00:23:15,950
My gosh. Are you crying?

275
00:23:17,240 --> 00:23:22,450
Please forgive this inadequate pupil!

276
00:23:25,900 --> 00:23:28,420
You'd better get up now.

277
00:23:31,920 --> 00:23:35,100
I did not expect to be forgiven easily.

278
00:23:47,210 --> 00:23:51,380
They say foolish students learn by being disciplined by their teachers.

279
00:23:51,380 --> 00:23:52,890
What's this?

280
00:23:52,890 --> 00:23:54,890
My heart is heavy.

281
00:23:54,890 --> 00:23:57,240
Please do not refuse and hit me with this—

282
00:23:57,240 --> 00:23:58,990
What the heck!

283
00:24:00,130 --> 00:24:01,880
What's this?

284
00:24:01,880 --> 00:24:04,720
Why would I hit you?

285
00:24:04,720 --> 00:24:06,920
Do you want to apologize that badly?

286
00:24:09,210 --> 00:24:12,790
- Yes. 
 - Can you do it differently, then?

287
00:24:12,790 --> 00:24:14,720
Please ask anything.

288
00:24:14,720 --> 00:24:16,580
Anything?

289
00:24:16,580 --> 00:24:18,250
Well...

290
00:24:18,250 --> 00:24:20,260
How about...

291
00:24:20,960 --> 00:24:23,010
you grant my wishes?

292
00:24:23,010 --> 00:24:25,250
- Wishes? 
 - I have three.

293
00:24:25,250 --> 00:24:28,750
You have three wishes?

294
00:24:28,750 --> 00:24:31,160
Why not? You play rock, paper, scissors three times

295
00:24:31,160 --> 00:24:34,060
and eat three times a day, too.

296
00:24:34,060 --> 00:24:35,890
What? You don't want to?

297
00:24:35,890 --> 00:24:38,260
Well, it is not that.

298
00:24:38,260 --> 00:24:41,430
I will grant your three wishes.

299
00:24:41,430 --> 00:24:43,900
- Go ahead and tell me. 
 - Really?

300
00:24:43,900 --> 00:24:46,730
Hold on. Well...

301
00:24:53,210 --> 00:24:55,400
My first wish is...

302
00:24:57,500 --> 00:25:01,050
What did you say just now?

303
00:25:01,050 --> 00:25:02,480
It's exactly as I said.

304
00:25:02,480 --> 00:25:06,230
Treat me rudely from now on.

305
00:25:06,230 --> 00:25:08,670
How could I dare to treat you rudely?

306
00:25:10,300 --> 00:25:11,640
- I cannot even speak about it. 
 - Yes, yes.

307
00:25:11,640 --> 00:25:14,450
What you said just now. Don't say things like that.

308
00:25:14,450 --> 00:25:18,300
"How could I dare to treat you..." Stuff like that.

309
00:25:18,300 --> 00:25:20,550
And not stepping on my shadow,

310
00:25:20,550 --> 00:25:22,910
sitting diagonally from me,

311
00:25:22,910 --> 00:25:25,120
and walking far away from me.

312
00:25:25,120 --> 00:25:27,460
Don't do stuff like that.

313
00:25:27,460 --> 00:25:29,660
Feel free to step on my shadow...

314
00:25:29,660 --> 00:25:31,250
walk side by side,

315
00:25:31,250 --> 00:25:34,400
sit in front of me, and we'll share a table, too.

316
00:25:34,400 --> 00:25:36,300
That's all you need to do.

317
00:25:37,730 --> 00:25:39,590
I will...

318
00:25:40,390 --> 00:25:42,780
- give it a try. 
 - What?

319
00:25:42,780 --> 00:25:45,090
It's my wish. You'd only try to do it?

320
00:25:46,760 --> 00:25:49,660
Okay, I will...

321
00:25:50,740 --> 00:25:52,670
do as you wish.

322
00:25:52,670 --> 00:25:54,150
Really?

323
00:25:54,150 --> 00:25:57,180
Shall we share the table immediately?

324
00:25:59,600 --> 00:26:01,340
L-Let us.

325
00:26:01,340 --> 00:26:04,870
I'll wait outside. Get changed and meet me outside.

326
00:26:05,820 --> 00:26:07,230
Okay.

327
00:26:09,820 --> 00:26:11,980
Take your time!

328
00:26:24,620 --> 00:26:26,050
Okay.

329
00:26:37,550 --> 00:26:42,930
♫  I just looked at you smiling in front of me  ♫

330
00:26:42,930 --> 00:26:47,100
♫  I want to hug you but I guess I'm scared  ♫

331
00:26:47,100 --> 00:26:51,550
♫  I hide it and try to push it away, but it's already here  ♫

332
00:26:51,550 --> 00:26:55,330
Yoon Bok, don't obsess over shadows.

333
00:26:55,330 --> 00:26:58,600
Just walk naturally. Naturally.

334
00:26:58,600 --> 00:27:00,370
Okay.

335
00:27:00,370 --> 00:27:01,600
Come.

336
00:27:01,600 --> 00:27:06,660
♫  Come back to my side anytime  ♫

337
00:27:06,660 --> 00:27:10,550
♫  For me, if it's you, it's all right  ♫

338
00:27:10,550 --> 00:27:16,220
♫  It's like the spring day I don't want to part with  ♫

339
00:27:16,220 --> 00:27:20,030
♫  Yes, if it’s just you, it’s all right  ♫

340
00:27:20,030 --> 00:27:22,250
What are you doing?

341
00:27:23,440 --> 00:27:27,450
I am looking for a place to face you.

342
00:27:27,450 --> 00:27:30,070
Where you are is fine.

343
00:27:30,070 --> 00:27:31,290
Here?

344
00:27:31,290 --> 00:27:32,970
Yes.

345
00:27:32,970 --> 00:27:36,910
♫  It's you who shines brightly  ♫

346
00:27:40,200 --> 00:27:46,600
I know this is late, but congratulations on taking a step closer to your dream.

347
00:27:46,600 --> 00:27:48,480
Thank you.

348
00:27:57,760 --> 00:27:59,460
Cheers.

349
00:27:59,460 --> 00:28:00,860
Okay.

350
00:28:18,870 --> 00:28:21,070
I will go back there if you feel uncomfortable—

351
00:28:21,070 --> 00:28:25,820
No, I'm okay. Just stay there.

352
00:28:37,200 --> 00:28:39,200
It is your father's wish.

353
00:28:39,200 --> 00:28:41,500
Please eat just one bite.

354
00:28:41,500 --> 00:28:43,930
Hurry!

355
00:28:43,930 --> 00:28:47,300
I have no appetite.

356
00:28:49,520 --> 00:28:52,700
You have never skipped a meal.

357
00:28:52,700 --> 00:28:55,150
But you have not been eating for days.

358
00:28:55,150 --> 00:28:58,780
What is going on, anyway?

359
00:28:58,780 --> 00:29:02,910
Just tell me what is going on!

360
00:29:02,910 --> 00:29:05,150
Come on!

361
00:29:07,790 --> 00:29:09,840
That's right. That's right.

362
00:29:12,060 --> 00:29:14,990
Gosh, what is it now?

363
00:29:17,490 --> 00:29:19,180
Yes.

364
00:29:21,350 --> 00:29:23,030
What?

365
00:29:23,030 --> 00:29:24,800
Se Ryeong is refusing to eat?

366
00:29:24,800 --> 00:29:27,990
I suppose she felt bothered that Yoon Bok had been

367
00:29:27,990 --> 00:29:30,450
visiting the village with a woman.

368
00:29:30,450 --> 00:29:33,190
Goodness gracious.

369
00:29:33,190 --> 00:29:36,370
Forgive me for saying this,

370
00:29:36,370 --> 00:29:41,260
but how about we discuss the family affairs soon?

371
00:29:42,350 --> 00:29:45,650
You mean Se Ryeong and Yoon Bok's marriage?

372
00:29:45,650 --> 00:29:50,220
Yes. They are both at the right age,

373
00:29:50,220 --> 00:29:54,190
and if we have something to celebrate, there will no longer

374
00:29:54,190 --> 00:29:58,680
be rumors of a nonsensical fashion show as well.

375
00:30:00,150 --> 00:30:06,310
You are not thinking of letting the fashion show happen, are you?

376
00:30:08,150 --> 00:30:12,370
I have a plan regarding that matter.

377
00:30:12,370 --> 00:30:14,760
I will think about the marriage.

378
00:30:14,760 --> 00:30:17,290
Do not worry and go back home.

