00:30:37,050 --> 00:30:39,960
Goodness, my legs.

384
00:30:39,960 --> 00:30:42,970
I opened the door because you kept asking if I was here.

385
00:30:42,970 --> 00:30:44,490
Why are you so surprised?

386
00:30:44,490 --> 00:30:48,540
No, it's nothing. I am not surprised at all.

387
00:30:49,540 --> 00:30:53,910
I have an urgent favor to ask you.

