00:31:02,800 --> 00:31:07,400
    
 Gosh, the building is taller than a mountain.

389
00:31:07,400 --> 00:31:11,670
My throat feels stuffy here after getting used to breathing fresh air.

390
00:31:11,670 --> 00:31:14,350
What's the problem? I like it.

