00:42:21,700 --> 00:42:25,070
Are you sure you're doing a good job?

504
00:42:25,070 --> 00:42:27,230
D-Do not move.

505
00:42:28,130 --> 00:42:29,430
Okay.

506
00:42:30,430 --> 00:42:34,250
It is almost done. Wait just a moment.

507
00:42:52,170 --> 00:42:54,230
Are you done? Let's see.

508
00:42:54,230 --> 00:42:55,540
I am not done yet.

509
00:42:55,540 --> 00:42:57,090
Just show it to me.

510
00:42:57,090 --> 00:43:01,250
I cannot. I cannot show you until I finish it.

511
00:43:01,250 --> 00:43:04,090
- Give it to me. 
 - I cannot.

512
00:43:05,560 --> 00:43:07,780
Huh? What's that?

513
00:43:10,440 --> 00:43:12,270
Wow.

514
00:43:13,070 --> 00:43:15,420
You did a good job.

515
00:43:17,850 --> 00:43:21,290
Please get back to your seat.

516
00:43:21,290 --> 00:43:22,810
Okay.

517
00:43:26,890 --> 00:43:28,080
Here you go.

518
00:43:28,080 --> 00:43:29,840
Thank you.

519
00:43:37,850 --> 00:43:40,270
Do you like it?

520
00:43:40,270 --> 00:43:45,360
Yes. It really feels like my dream came true.

521
00:43:45,360 --> 00:43:50,290
I had fun since I got to draw again, thanks to you.

522
00:43:50,290 --> 00:43:52,110
Really?

523
00:43:58,750 --> 00:44:01,970
What is your third wish?

